                <h1>Discovering Olan Mills: A Legacy in Family Photography</h1>
                <p>Olan Mills was founded in 1932 by the photographer Olan Mills and initially gained recognition in family portrait studios across the United States. The company was known for its approachable photography style and strong emphasis on customer care, expanding into various photography services and becoming a staple in American family photography culture.</p>
